{"lemma":"كِتابٌ","slug":"كِتابٌ","root":"ك.ت.ب","root_slug":"ك-ت-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ك-ت-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"كِتاب","root":"كتب","pos":"N","occurrence_count":260},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":9},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n36634","n42947","n36638"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%83%D9%90%D8%AA%D8%A7%D8%A8%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of كَتَبَ (kataba) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb","obsolete"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of كَاتَبَ (kātaba) (form III)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"],"examples":[{"text":"وَٱلَّذِينَ يَبْتَغُونَ ٱلْكِتَابَ مِمَّا مَلَكَتْ أَيْمَانُكُمْ فَكَاتِبُوهُمْ","english":"And those who seek a contract (for eventual emancipation) from among whom your right hands possess - then make a contract with them"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"book"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"letter, note, paper, piece of writing, message","examples":[{"text":"قَالَتْ يَا أَيُّهَا ٱلْمَلَأُ إِنِّي أُلْقِيَ إِلَيَّ كِتَابٌ كَرِيمٌ ۝ إِنَّهُ مِنْ سُلَيْمَانَ وَإِنَّهُ بِسْمِ ٱللَّٰهِ ٱلرَّحْمَـٰنِ ٱلرَّحِيمِ ۝ أَلَّا تَعْلُوا عَلَيَّ وَأْتُونِي مُسْلِمِينَ ۝","english":"She said, O eminent ones, indeed, to me has been delivered a noble letter. Indeed, it is from Solomon, and indeed, it is: 'In the name of God, the Entirely Merciful, the Especially Merciful, be not haughty with me but come to me in submission.'"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"the Scripture, the Qur'an or the Bible","examples":[{"text":"الْكِتَاب","english":"the Qur'an; the Bible"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"record, document, deed, contract"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a marriage contract."},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of كَاتِب (kātib, “writer”)","tags":["form-of","plural"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a traditional school for teaching Qur'an"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ki.taːb/","[keˈtæːb]","[kɪˈt̪aːb]","[kiˈtæːb]","[kɪˈt̪ɑːb]","[kiˈt̪ɛːb]","[kteːb]","[kt̪ɛːb]","[ktæːb]","[kt̪ɑːb]","/kut.taːb/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n36634","headword_ar":"كِتَابٌ","root":"ktb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[inf. n. of 1, q. v. ―         -b2-  as a subst.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing in which,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"on which, one writes:"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a book:"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a written piece of paper"},{"kind":"text","text":"or ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a record,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"register;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a written mandate;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of skin:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a writing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"writ,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing written;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"katiybapN","text_ar":"كَتِيبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": and both are applied also to the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"revelation from above:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a letter,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"epistle, which a person writes and sends:"},{"kind":"text","text":"sometimes made fem., as meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHiyfapN","text_ar":"صَحِيفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": AA says, I heard an Arab of the desert, of El-Yemen, say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN laguwbN jaA='atohu kitaAbiY faA@HotaqarahaA","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ لَغُوبٌ جَا=ءَتْهُ كِتَابِى فَا@حْتَقَرَهَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is stupid: my letter came to him, and he despised it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so I said, Dost thou say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jA'th","text_ar":"جاءته"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ktAbY","text_ar":"كتابى"},{"kind":"text","text":"? and he replied, Is it not a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SHyfp","text_ar":"صحيفة"},{"kind":"text","text":"? (Msb.) Pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kutubN","text_ar":"كُتُبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kutobN","text_ar":"كُتْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A revealed scripture."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) [Whence"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aholu kitaAbK","text_ar":"اَهْلُ كِتَابٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"People having a revealed scripture:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aholu AlkitaAbi","text_ar":"اَهْلُ الكِتَابِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The people of the Bible."},{"kind":"text","text":"See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aholN","text_ar":"اَهْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlktAb","text_ar":"الكتاب"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taworAp","text_ar":"تَوْراة"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Pentateuch,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Mosaic Law:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the Gospel,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Book of the Gospels: the Scriptures of the Jews and Christians:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Expositions of the Kur, passim:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the Kur-án."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-  See also 3.       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kitaAbN","text_ar":"كِتَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[inf. n., or subst.: see 1]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Divine prescript, appointment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ordinance: judgment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sentence: fatal decree,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"predestination."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA^aqoDiyan~a bayonakumaA bikitaAbi All~`hi","text_ar":"لَاَقْضِيَنَّ بَيْنَكُمَا بِكِتَابِ اللّٰهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I will assuredly determine,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"judge, between you two according to the judgment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sentence, of God, which hath"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2591},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"been revealed in his book."},{"kind":"text","text":"A trad., not relating to the Kur-án. (TA.) El-Jaadee says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"yaA A@bonapa Eam~iY kitaAbu All~`hi A^axorajaniY\n                      \n                     \n                        Eanokumo wahalo A^amonafan~a All~`ha maA faEalaA"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"O daughter of my paternal uncle! the decree of God hath expelled me from you: and could I indeed forbid God to do what He hath done?"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (S.) [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlkitaAbu AlA^aw~alu","text_ar":"الكِتَابُ الاَوَّلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The first writing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the register of God's decrees"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (M and K voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHobalN","text_ar":"مَحْبَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.) ―         -b2-  A receptacle for ink. (K)."}],"source_refs":["K"]},{"entry_id":"n42947","headword_ar":"كِتَابٌ","root":"ktb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaqodN","text_ar":"عَقْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The ceremony"},{"kind":"text","text":"(not certificate)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a marriage-contract."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"katabuwAkitaAbahu EalaY","text_ar":"كَتَبُواكِتَابَهُ عَلَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnapK","text_ar":"فُلَانَةٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They performed the ceremony of the contract of his marriage to such a woman"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EqdwA Eaqodahu","text_ar":"عقدوا عَقْدَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"). ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aholu AlkitaAbi","text_ar":"اَهْلُ الكِتَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aholN","text_ar":"اَهْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n36638","headword_ar":"كُتَّابٌ","root":"ktb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"makotabN","text_ar":"مَكْتَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"-A2-  The same, (S, K,) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kuv~aAbN","text_ar":"كُثَّابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v., but the former is the more approved: (S: the reverse, however, is said in the TA; and MF says that some authors altogether reject"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kt~Ab","text_ar":"كتّاب"},{"kind":"text","text":", with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t","text_ar":"ت"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the sense here following:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A kind of small, round-headed, arrow, with which boys learn to shoot."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D9%83%D8%AA%D8%A7%D8%A8/","headword_ar":"كتاب","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_18","lexicon_en":"Al-Sharīf al-Jurjānī, Kitāb al-Taʿrīfāt (d. 1413 CE)","lexicon_ar":"كتاب التعريفات للشريف الجرجاني","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=23514#3307c0","body_html":"<span>الكتاب المبين: هو اللوح المحفوظ، وهو المراد بقوله تعالى: {وَلا رَطْبٍ وَلا يَابِسٍ إِلَّا فِي كِتَابٍ مُبِينٍ} .</span>"}]}}